<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Others</title>
    <script src="/js/tailwindcss.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/page.css">
    <style>
        .hero-section {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 50vh;
            background-color: #2d3748;
        }
        .searchbox {
            position: absolute;
            transform: translate(-50%, 0%);
            width: 80%;
            max-width: 700px;
            padding: 0.75rem;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            border-radius: 25px;
            border: none;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            color: white;
            outline: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .searchbox:focus {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        }
        .app-card-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 16px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .app-card {
            background-color: #1a202c;
            border-radius: 25px;
            padding: 15px;
            width: 180px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            border: 2px solid #4a5568;
        }
        .app-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }
        .app-card img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .app-card h3 {
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .app-card p {
            color: #cbd5e0;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
        }
        footer {
            background-color: #2d3748;
            color: #cbd5e0;
            padding: 1rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-900 font-sans min-h-screen flex flex-col">
    <button class="back-button fixed top-5 left-5 z-50 bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold py-2 px-4 rounded-lg shadow-lg transform transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out flex items-center space-x-2" onclick="window.location.href='/wkt'">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path>
        </svg>
        <span>戻る</span>
    </button>

    <div class="section flex-grow text-center pt-24 pb-10">
      
        <div class="mt-6 mb-10 px-4">
          <input type="text" id="search" placeholder="YouTubeサイトを検索..." class="w-full max-w-md p-2 border rounded-lg shadow-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 text-black">
        </div>
  
        <section class="py-10 px-4 bg-gray-800 rounded-t-3xl mx-2 shadow-lg h-full">

            <div class="mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-white text-2xl font-bold mb-6 border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-4 text-left">直接搭載しているYouTubeサイト集</h2>
                <div class="app-card-container">
                    <div class="app-card">
                        <a href="/other/others/sia" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                        <img src="https://uploads.scratch.mit.edu/projects/thumbnails/1218808422.png">
                        </a>
                        <h3 class="app-title">しあtube</h3>
                        <p class="app-description">バージョン1.5.4 (2026/03/18時点)<br><br>siawaseokさんが開発しているYouTubeサイト</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="app-card">
                        <a href="/other/others/xerox#/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                        <img src="https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://youtube-pro.com.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/youtubepro.png&output=png">
                        </a>
                        <h3 class="app-title">XeroxYT-NT</h3>
                        <p class="app-description">v5 (2026/03/07時点)<br><br>soranousさんが開発しているYouTubeサイト<br>EducationのパラメーターをToka_Kun_のものに変えています。</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="app-card">
                        <a href="/other/others/wista" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                        <img src="https://uploads.scratch.mit.edu/projects/thumbnails/1276740034.png">
                        </a>
                        <h3 class="app-title">Wista</h3>
                        <p class="app-description">woolisbestさんが開発しているYouTubeサイト</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="app-card">
                        <a href="/other/others/labo5#/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                        <img src="https://uploads.scratch.mit.edu/projects/thumbnails/1224846250.png">
                        </a>
                        <h3 class="app-title">Re: LABO5</h3>
                        <p class="app-description">minoさんが開発したYouTubeサイトであるLABO5をToka_Kun_が改善したやつです。2026/03/30追記:サーバーの負荷がヤバそうだったのでEducationに変更しました。</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="app-card">
                        <a href="/other/others/player" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                        <img src="https://uploads.scratch.mit.edu/projects/thumbnails/1264052367.png">
                        </a>
                        <h3 class="app-title">YouTube 埋め込み再生ツール</h3>
                        <p class="app-description">Toka_Kun_が開発したYouTubeを埋め込みで視聴することだけを限界まで極めたツールです。実は再生リストなどにも対応しています。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <hr class="border-gray-700 my-10">

            <div>
                <h2 class="text-white text-2xl font-bold mb-6 border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-4 text-left">各YouTubeサイトのリンク集</h2>
                <div class="app-card-container">
                    <div class="app-card">
                        <a href="#">
                            <img src="https://uploads.scratch.mit.edu/projects/thumbnails/1297245033.png">
                        </a>
                        <h3 class="app-title">MIN-Tube-Pro</h3>
                        <p class="app-description">minoさんが開発しているYouTubeサイト</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="app-card">
                        <a href="#">
                            <img src="https://uploads.scratch.mit.edu/projects/thumbnails/1295714014.png">
                        </a>
                        <h3 class="app-title">YouTube Plus+</h3>
                        <p class="app-description">yuto_110さんが開発しているYouTubeサイト</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </section>
    </div>

    <footer class="mt-auto">
        <p>♪( ´▽｀)</p>
    </footer>
  
    <script>
        const searchInput = document.getElementById('search');
        const tools = document.querySelectorAll('.app-card');
        searchInput.addEventListener('input', function() {
            const searchText = searchInput.value.toLowerCase();

            tools.forEach(tool => {
                const title = tool.querySelector('.app-title').textContent.toLowerCase();
                const description = tool.querySelector('.app-description').textContent.toLowerCase();
                if (title.includes(searchText) || description.includes(searchText)) {
                    tool.style.display = '';
                } else {
                    tool.style.display = 'none';
                }
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
